record.title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 1644
record.narrative:
REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 1644 -- (House of Representatives - September 19, 2007)

[Page: H10551]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent that the gentleman from Wisconsin's (Mr. Ryan) name be removed as a cosponsor of H.R. 1644. Our staff inadvertently, mistakenly added his name.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from New Jersey?
